Idea - Forum with implementing democratic decision making within a group

Create Users

User - Admin can create a group with a specific agenda.

Users can join group and discuss the agenda and propose action items.

Users in group can amend the proposal, discuss and then send it to vote.

Visualize the voting with a bar graph or pie chart.

Each proposal will have a status of pass, fail, in process.



